The 2019 MyBroadband Cloud Conference will showcase the best cloud services available to South African companies and feature excellent speakers and exhibitors. This year, the MyBroadband Cloud Conference will be hosted on 6 June 2019 at the Gallagher Convention Centre in Midrand, Gauteng. It is the premier cloud event in South Africa and the meeting place for the country’s IT and cloud community. Delegates will learn more about a business’s journey into the cloud and what should be done to make the most of the latest developments in the cloud, hosting, data centre, and cloud telecoms markets. All delegates will also receive a voucher booklet with special deals and promotions on cloud and hosting products and services for your business. The 2019 MyBroadband Cloud Conference will feature speakers from South Africa’s top cloud and hosting providers. These speakers include Liquid Telecom CEO Reshaad Sha, Connection Telecom MD David Meintjes, Teraco CFO Jan Hnizdo, and Microsoft cloud specialist Kevin George. Delegates will also hear from VMware’s cloud manager Dave Funnell, Schneider Electric regional executive Derek Friend, and Google Cloud specialist and Siatik CEO Brett StClair. Registrations for the 2019 MyBroadband Cloud Conference are open and MyBroadband readers can register at a big discount using the voucher code below. Please note that a limited number of tickets will be available using this discount code.